\begin_layout Standard
This document is an early development version for 
\series bold
Starlit Skies
\series default
, a roleplaying system about magical girls trying to make the best of the
 end of the world.
 The system is overall meant as a successor to the Magical Burst 3rd Draft
 lineage of systems - one that was effectively abandoned by its original
 author after they converted their system to use the PbtA framework.
 As such, it follows up on Fact's efforts to finish that branch of the system
 in his Project Rebirth and Burst Rewrite systems.
\end_layout

